  "evidence_excerpts": [
    {
      "text": "Consider what the appropriate response to such a report would be.\n\nActually the report is merely a confirm, part of a precise feedback system (this is why I had to do eleven drafts, specifically of the last section). The corrective circuit itself was the two of us, Thomas & me, doing the plumbing, the analysis; that's part of its job. This explains the sacredness about Thomas; he is a microform of the corrective circuit (the Lord of Light), so in a sense the Lord himself entered this world, as T",
      "matched_alias": "Bill",
      "term_id": "TERM_bill",
      "term_name": "Bill",
      "term_slug": "bill"
    }
  ],
